Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}高中生 南極…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:01:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼是燙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為奶奶說 現在還是五月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是五月 燙的東西還是燙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要冷飲 還有茶點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也想吃點布丁什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們不覺得我們這樣很怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很怪？是你要我們做那種計劃的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有臉嫌棄喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是啊 妳知道我有多羞恥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也想不出別的方法了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那種事也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女高中生…去南極！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:36.13,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H474F4C&\pos(230,14)\frz340.6}「女高中生去南極！」現役女高中生歌星，將與民間觀測隊一道進行為期三個月的南極之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:39.34,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H474F4C&\frz340.6\move(230,14,258,-144,0,3196)}「女高中生去南極！」現役女高中生歌星，將與民間觀測隊一道進行為期三個月的南極之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}預計今年出發的民間南極觀測隊日前宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一名現役女高中生將與拍攝組一同隨隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這名女高中生就是歌星白石結月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她的南極之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以及在昭和基地的生活將進行網路直播
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被搶先了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前那兩個隊員什麼都沒提
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是提了 這傢伙會吵翻天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報導人員 記者 同行人員 我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石結月 她的事務所…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打電話到這
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打電話幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟對方商量能不能帶我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是南極觀測隊員的女兒 也是高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還非常了解南極
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你自己打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個 我覺得我不太合適 我怕生而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好像漸漸理解她的性格了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我按
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我做不到做不到做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想去南極的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打擾一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不公平 把難事推給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這話我原封不動地還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.41,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是小淵澤報瀨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好 我叫做白石結月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:03:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 這名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}維基上找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}五歲起參演CM等 扮演兒童角色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}關注者3.8萬？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:27.91,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}フォローバックが止まらない♪　フォローワー…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:27.91,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回關不停歇 關注者…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去年憑藉《回關不停歇》一曲作為歌手出道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太羞恥了 有點想死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快拍一張
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隨便上傳到社群是侵犯我的肖像權
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:38.71,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur3\fs33}我能找張彩紙求個簽名和掌印嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你當她是大力士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:39.71,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※相撲館裡，印有大力士掌印的彩紙是熱賣紀念品。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說你為什麼會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能替我去南極嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極 你想去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去哪洩漏的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}BBS？推特？發動態？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.77,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒說出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前觀測隊在新宿開聯歡會的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也受到邀請了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那時候聽說了你們的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但為什麼要找人替代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}簡單來說 我不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是北海道出生的 不喜歡天寒地凍的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:20.00,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\b0\fs20\1c&H3F3E40&\pos(684,240)\frz293.5}電視節目企劃書
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:20.00,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fn華康POP1體W9\bord0\b0\fs40\1c&H3F3E40&\frz293.5\pos(638,222)}女高中生\N去南極
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:20.00,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\b0\fs20\1c&H3F3E40&\frx340\fry10\pos(432,358)\frz294.6}青空電視台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果要找高中女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算不是我也對節目主題沒有影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就說了吧 按我的計劃來萬無一失！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.07,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼亂來 什麼荒唐 都你說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.86,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不在計劃內吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不是很順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啊南極 能去南極了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等我 企鵝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等我 極光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像很痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 她是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:05:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是唯一的出口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}涼鞋借穿一下 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:23.44,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康楷書體W5\bord0\1c&H474343&\org(807.999,421.333)\frx2\fry10\pos(993.333,213.334)\frz21.58}新\N　\N北\N海\N道\N姑\N娘\N企\N劃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:23.44,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康楷書體W5\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H474343&\frz14.62\frx10\fry12\org(808.666,426)\pos(804.666,298)}製\N作\N人\N‧\N經\N紀\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是結月的經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫白石民子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也是她的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是說很多次我不要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這可由不得你說 這是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已經說過讓給她們去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你以為你一句話就能改嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我收回了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在南極做報導吧 她就不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看她多漂亮 跟個藝人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報導俐落嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…現在…在南極…天氣…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.94,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 聽不清你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 我來報導 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家好 我在南極喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日本的大家看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你哪裡上鏡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說得好直
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要你多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吧 那我只好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.76,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\fs30\1c&H395A56&\3c&H70CB8F&\frz321.5\pos(800,164)}嗯…雖然我也想去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.76,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs25\1c&HB7CECF&\pos(562,42)\frz320.3}愛菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.76,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H58707C&\frz320.3\pos(524,184)}還不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.76,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs25\1c&HB7CECF&\frz320.3\pos(482,222)}悠里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.76,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H58707C&\frz320.3\pos(352,296)}下週日呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打 打擾一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然這麼說可能有點怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過 能和我做朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.95,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(100,0)\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\1c&H304945&\frx334\fry346\pos(650,174)\frz350.5}抱歉…給我點時間再答覆你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟你說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等你升到高二 會給你多留休息時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}連一年都不能忍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別擔心 會給你留足備考時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想管什麼升學考
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我上高中又不是為了考試！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還以為有奇蹟發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是報瀨口才好點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那日向你不也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以別再提了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.61,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有這麼受傷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎光臨…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說服她？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯 那女生好像就是不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你們能說服她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就通過廣播電視台的門路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}推薦你們作為隨行人員入團 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說 只要能讓她答應去…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是結月已經不在這裡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我聽說她週日在東京有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以會在飯店住到週六
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}週五週六 就兩天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒時間磨蹭了 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經過10點了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就明早上學前 5點？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 你要去嚇醒她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就6點？7點？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你給個時間啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她既然那麼不情願
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定有很不想去的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道不是因為她怕冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她說過是「簡單來說」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以肯定有其他難以啟齒的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向好成熟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼原因？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我們就是要先問清楚這點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原因啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}糟了 拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自我嫌棄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實我也覺得你說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但最後總是先考慮自己的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能沒有為別人著想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在才發現？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開個玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俗話說得好 信念堅定與固執己見只有一線之隔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天不去打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那要不要一起去吃點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極啊…去得成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 下次再約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}305號房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼辦 跟…跟蹤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟著她沒意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}裝一下 就裝碰巧遇上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 你住在這裡啊 要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讀書？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 沒上的課我得自己補上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡有自助飲料 還能待到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真勤奮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們想談南極的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 我這邊還沒什麼進展
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們是這麼想沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過在這之前 有點事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你為什麼不想去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有那麼奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為去了南極就能看到企鵝 還有冰山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說不定還能看到極光…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我媽媽跟你們說了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要你們說服我去 之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:11:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不打自招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過也確實有事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想知道你為什麼不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不想說的話…不勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想你們是不會懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是光現在沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是從來 從來沒有過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:36.94,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\blur8\t(0,300,0\blur0)\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H7F7CA5&\t(0,4180,0\fs25)\frz8.181\move(276,216,332,274,0,4154)}恭喜{\1c&HB1BD94&}白石結月小妹妹\N{\1c&H7F7CA5&}上電視啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我從四歲起就做兒童演員了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但因為工作忙 幾乎沒時間和朋友玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我意識過來 生活已經陷入了惡性循環
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我從來沒有和朋友吵過架
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵架的對象總是只有媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我想上了高中 一定要交幾個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}參加社團 打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放學後和朋友去買東西吃 唱卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:13.64,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H555B5F&\frz332.2\pos(662,144)}悠里與愛菜與結月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:13.64,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs15\1c&H9DA6A8&\frz332.2\pos(656,232)}悠里邀請你加入群組
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 下次我們三個一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有 能一起拍張照嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結月這麼有名 我想給朋友們看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也要 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎 那拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第一印象是很重要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果現在不努力融入進去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這些朋友關係和小圈子 都會固化定型的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然好想抱緊你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我懂你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也很討厭新學期開始呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你才不懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為你們都是好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們幾個才認識一個月不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也沒在一起玩過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是想去同一個地方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少現在來說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉打擾到這麼晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望你媽媽能理解你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才要謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟你們聊完 心情也平靜點了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以結論到底是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼結論
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你忘了嗎 我們是來說服結月的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 但要是結月拒絕去 報瀨就能代替她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說服她的話 就能一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 但要是結月拒絕去 報瀨就能代替她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No 思緒一片混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪有那麼複雜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是她拒絕去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定有別的藝人能替代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我們只有說服她這條路可走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得這樣子也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:47.80,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3E4638&\frz309.4\pos(266,346)}抱歉…下次有時間再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.42,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H3E4638&\frz309.4\pos(454,428)}抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.42,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H3E4638&\pos(380,492)\frz308.3}下次有時間再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是第一次 有人那樣對待我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朋友就是像那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們一起去南極吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們在做什麼啊 會被罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別廢話了 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}風很大 快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 我還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把手伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好怪的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:04.39,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\b0\bord0\fs25\1c&HBFBAA6&\frz340.6\move(516,446,520,284,34,3246)}愛菜退出了群組
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:04.39,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\b0\bord0\fs25\1c&HBCB8A2&\frz340.6\move(440,584,444,418,0,3246)}悠里退出了群組
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:43.97,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そっと記した夢　言い訳ばかりして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:54.69,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ほったらかしにしていた　叶うのが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:19:03.33,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何があるのかも　何が変わるのかも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:08.87,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}行ってみなきゃ分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:17.01,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあ　一歩前に　踏み出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:23.35,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大きな夢を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:27.85,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハルカ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:32.44,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真っ白な世界に　残したいな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:37.19,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}最初の足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:42.57,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大きな夢を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:46.99,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハルカ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:51.75,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真っ白な世界に　残したいな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:56.63,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}最初の足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:20:06.26,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界の最果てで　転がっていく太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:12.06,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}南風はやがて島を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:16.57,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}髪を揺らす
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:36.38,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}小さな夢を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:41.09,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}願えた　ツヨクツヨク
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:43.59,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}履き慣れたスニーカー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:50.22,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}紐をギュッと締め直して
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:55.77,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}でかい夢を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:21:00.23,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハルカ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:04.86,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}波に揺られてかたふりして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:09.87,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}進んでいくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:14.25,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}宇宙より遠くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:43.97,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}偷偷記下了夢想 卻只找了一堆藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:54.69,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想到自己總是忘記夢想 就怕去實現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:19:03.33,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}怕出什麼事 怕有什麼變故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:08.87,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}但駐足不前 就什麼都明白不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:17.01,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向前一步 邁出勇敢的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:23.35,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想實現心底大大的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:27.85,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遙遠不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:32.44,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想在那一片純白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:37.19,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}留下我最初的腳印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:42.57,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想實現心底大大的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:46.99,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遙遠不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:51.75,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想在那一片純白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:56.63,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}留下我最初的腳印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:20:06.26,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}紅紅的一輪夕陽 沉入了世界的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:12.06,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}海面南風跨越萬千島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:16.57,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}吹動起我的髮梢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:36.38,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想實現心底小小的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:41.09,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用力再用力 向神明許願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:43.59,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}穿上熟悉的運動鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:50.22,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}緊緊地繫好鞋帶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:55.77,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想實現心底大大的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:21:00.23,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遙遠不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:04.86,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就在波濤之中舉杯高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:09.87,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}繼續一步步前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:14.25,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}去比宇宙更遙遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就說太早了吧 人家還穿著睡衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是報瀨說要來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒得選擇啊 之後還要去東京呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}東京？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 聽說結月要去東京工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果方便的話 想跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 來之前沒打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰叫這傢伙沒問聯絡方式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的錯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:18:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎 那我們就去東京的南極…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的錯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還能是誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但提議一起去的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是說 帶上她們三個我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不然我可不答應去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 結月 出發囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}企…企鵝！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毛茸茸的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毛茸茸 毛茸茸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 這裡可以進來耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡好擠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現役的是更新型的雪地車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}微速直線前進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.48,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※此處是海軍用語。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這可不是船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:20:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雙層床只剩上層的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}室內會控制在20度以上 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外面會是零下10度 肯定會冷到流鼻涕的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家再靠近點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真正的極光會更漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽跟我說過 美到讓人看了都想哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是極光可不容易見到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那如果我們能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能就是世界僅有的 在南極看極光的高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對啊 這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會有點想死呢！
Comment: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:20.81,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}長いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:31.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:37.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}間違っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:48.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　僕は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:59.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}汚れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:10.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言葉も　きっと見つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:15.91,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:21.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:20.81,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}尋找著漫長隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:31.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向著泛著微光氣味的方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:37.33,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走錯了 也別忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:48.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}從這裡開始 我將踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:59.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}緊緊捏住手心裡 髒髒的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:10.32,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}沒說出口的話 我也一定會找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:15.91,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}隨你們嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:21.25,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 邁出腳步
